org.transitime.core.travelTimes

Class TravelTimeInfoWithHowSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.transitime.core.travelTimes.TravelTimeInfo
      • org.transitime.core.travelTimes.TravelTimeInfoWithHowSet

  • public class TravelTimeInfoWithHowSet
extends TravelTimeInfo
    Extends TravelTimeInfo class but adds how the travel time was set. This way can see if travel time set via AVL data directly, is for a different trip, or is for a different service class, etc.
    Author:
    SkiBu Smith
